@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.02 - wp.exp((v1 + 0.62 / v0 + 0.37)))
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.25 * v1 + 0.68) + wp.exp(tmp + 0.94)) * (v0 / (tmp + 0.73 / tmp + 0.43)))
    tmp = ((v1 / (tmp + 0.27 + v0 + 0.81)) * ((tmp + 0.74 - v1 + 0.21) - (v0 + 0.19 - v1 + 0.71)))
    v2 = 0.54
    v1 = (wp.abs(v2) * (wp.cos(v2 + 0.91) + wp.exp(v0 + 0.32)))
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
